cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper presents a real-time monocular camera relocalization system using a convolutional neural network. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the system can be used for robot navigation and localization. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses an end-to-end learning approach with a deep convolutional neural network. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper presents an AI-based solution for camera relocalization. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with image-based camera pose estimation.
